title: SWE: Flirting for Dummies
itunes:title: SWE: Flirting for Dummies
itunes:subtitle: Emily discusses the best flirting practices to adopt and the sacred duties of the Wingman. Menace and Emily talk Kony 2012, joining forces with Kris Jenner, and the 'Panty Dropper' recipe.
description:
Emily and Menace both have sex in the same weekend, but with different people of course. Menace has sex in the shower and the girl didn’t faint this time. A recipe for “panty droppers” a drink that might be true to it’s name,  flirting techniques and the sacred duties of the wingman.
